<section style="position:relative;padding:120px 32px;overflow:hidden;background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 20%, rgba(255,45,149,.15), transparent 50%), radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 80%, rgba(124,77,255,.15), transparent 50%), var(--tron-void);">
    <div class="tron-grid-bg" style="position:absolute;inset:0;opacity:.4;"></div>
    <div style="position:relative;max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:80px;align-items:center;" class="retro-metalx-grid">
        <div style="position:relative;aspect-ratio:1/1;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;">
            <div class="tron-spin-slow" style="width:90%;aspect-ratio:1/1;border-radius:50%;background:repeating-radial-gradient(circle, #000 0 2px, #0a0a14 2px 3px),radial-gradient(circle,#ff2d95 0%, #7c4dff 40%, #030711 70%);border:2px solid var(--tron-gold);box-shadow:var(--glow-mag), var(--glow-gold);position:relative;">
                <div style="position:absolute;top:50%;left:50%;width:30%;aspect-ratio:1/1;margin-top:-15%;margin-left:-15%;border-radius:50%;background:radial-gradient(circle,#d4af37,#8a7020);box-shadow:inset 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,.5), var(--glow-gold);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-direction:column;">
                    <span style="font-family:var(--font-display);color:#030711;font-size:clamp(14px,2vw,22px);font-weight:700;">METAL-X</span>
                    <span style="font-family:var(--font-ui);font-size:9px;letter-spacing:.3em;color:#030711;">RECORDS</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div style="position:absolute;top:8%;right:5%;width:35%;height:2px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,#d4af37,#f5d76e,#d4af37);transform:rotate(32deg);transform-origin:right center;box-shadow:0 0 6px rgba(212,175,55,.5);">
                <span style="position:absolute;left:0;top:-6px;width:14px;height:14px;background:#d4af37;border-radius:50%;box-shadow:var(--glow-gold);"></span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div>
            <div style="font-family:var(--font-ui);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.4em;color:var(--tron-magenta);text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:16px;">Side B · Music Division</div>
            <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:clamp(48px,6vw,80px);line-height:1;margin:0 0 24px;color:var(--fg-1);">Metal-X<br><span class="tron-gold-foil">Project</span></h2>
            <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:19px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--fg-2);font-style:italic;margin:0 0 32px;">
                "ห้องปฏิบัติการเพลงและมิวสิควิดีโอ — where the studio's engineers moonlight as composers. Broadcasting on YouTube since MMXX."
            </p>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
                <a href="#" class="tron-btn tron-btn-gold" style="text-decoration:none;">Visit Channel →</a>
                <a href="#" class="tron-btn" style="text-decoration:none;color:var(--tron-magenta);border-color:var(--tron-magenta);box-shadow:0 0 12px rgba(255,45,149,.3);">Meet the Band</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <style>@media(max-width:860px){.retro-metalx-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr !important;}}</style>
</section>
